and improve overall circulation. Using long, flowing strokes, gentle kneading, and rhythmic tapping techniques, this massage helps release tension, reduce muscle stiffness, and leave your body feeling refreshed and energized. It’s perfect for anyone looking to unwind and experience deep relaxation.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nRelieves muscle tension & stiffness |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nReduces stress and fatigue |\r\nEnhances flexibility |\r\nPromotes overall relaxation"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 10, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Deep Tissue Massage 💪", "image": "", "image_url": "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1169228621/photo/young-man-enjoying-massage-at-spa.webp?a=1&b=1&s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=Lt8BMpL8nlr3uj2m9lahykIwSFc2DmR-yE3KF5B4VwE=", "description": "Deep Tissue Massage is a powerful therapeutic treatment that targets the deeper layers of muscles and connective tissues. Using slow, firm pressure and focused techniques, it helps release chronic muscle tension, reduce pain, and improve mobility. This massage is ideal for those with muscle stiffness, injuries, or long-term physical stress.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nRelieves chronic muscle pain |\r\nBreaks down knots & tension |\r\nImproves posture and flexibility |\r\nSupports injury recovery |\r\nEnhances blood flow to deep tissues"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 11, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Balinese Massage 🌺", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/8496786/pexels-photo-8496786.jpeg", "description": "Balinese Massage is a luxurious, full-body therapy that blends gentle stretches, acupressure, and aromatherapy oils to create a deeply relaxing and revitalizing experience. Originating from Bali, this massage uses a combination of smooth strokes and firm pressure to ease muscle tension, improve circulation, and restore energy balance—leaving you feeling completely refreshed and renewed.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nRelieves deep muscle tension |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nPromotes relaxation & stress relief |\r\nEnhances energy flow in the body |\r\nNourishes skin with essential oils"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 12, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Thai Yoga Massage 🧘‍♀️", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/6188125/pexels-photo-6188125.jpeg", "description": "Thai Yoga Massage is a unique and energizing therapy that combines assisted stretching, acupressure, and rhythmic movements—often described as “lazy yoga.” Performed without oils, this massage improves flexibility, relieves deep tension, and restores the body’s natural energy flow, leaving you feeling both relaxed and revitalized.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nImproves flexibility & body movement |\r\nRelieves joint and muscle stiffness |\r\nBoosts energy levels |\r\nEnhances blood circulation |\r\nReduces stress and promotes balance"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 13, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Body Scrub & Polish ✨", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/36436443/pexels-photo-36436443.jpeg", "description": "Body Scrub & Polish is a luxurious skin-rejuvenating treatment that gently exfoliates dead skin cells and deeply nourishes your skin. Using natural scrubs, essential oils, and hydrating lotions, this therapy leaves your skin feeling incredibly soft, smooth, and radiant. It’s the perfect way to refresh your body and achieve a healthy, glowing look.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nRemoves dead skin cells & impurities |\r\nReveals smoother, glowing skin |\r\nImproves skin texture & tone |\r\nBoosts blood circulation |\r\nDeeply hydrates and nourishes skin"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 14, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Dry Thai Massage", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/6188120/pexels-photo-6188120.jpeg", "description": "Dry Thai Massage is a traditional therapeutic treatment performed without oils, focusing on deep stretching, acupressure, and rhythmic compressions. Often called “passive yoga,” this massage helps improve flexibility, release muscle stiffness, and restore the body’s natural energy flow. It is ideal for those who prefer a more active and energizing massage experience.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nEnhances flexibility & mobility |\r\nRelieves muscle and joint stiffness |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nBoosts energy and vitality |\r\nReduces stress and body fatigue"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 15, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Cream & Oil Massage", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/6628606/pexels-photo-6628606.jpeg", "description": "Cream & Oil Massage is a soothing and nourishing therapy that combines the richness of body creams with the smooth glide of essential oils. This treatment deeply hydrates the skin while providing a relaxing massage experience that relieves stress and muscle tension. It’s perfect for achieving soft, glowing skin along with complete body relaxation.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nDeeply moisturizes and nourishes skin |\r\nRelieves muscle tension and fatigue |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nEnhances skin softness & glow |\r\nPromotes relaxation and stress relief"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 16, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Hot Stone Massage", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/5378219/pexels-photo-5378219.jpeg", "description": "Hot Stone Massage is a deeply relaxing therapy that uses smooth, heated stones placed on key points of the body. The warmth penetrates deep into the muscles, helping to release tension, improve circulation, and promote a sense of calm. Combined with gentle massage techniques, this treatment melts away stress and leaves you feeling completely rejuvenated.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nRelieves deep muscle tension |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nPromotes deep relaxation |\r\nReduces stress and anxiety |\r\nHelps ease muscle stiffness and pain"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 17, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Bamboo Massage", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/9335986/pexels-photo-9335986.jpeg", "description": "Bamboo Massage is a unique deep-tissue therapy that uses smooth, heated bamboo sticks to knead and roll out muscle tension. The firm pressure from the bamboo helps reach deeper layers of muscles, improving circulation and relieving stiffness while promoting a sense of relaxation and balance.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nRelieves deep muscle tension |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nEnhances flexibility & mobility |\r\nReduces stress and fatigue |\r\nHelps in body contouring and toning"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 18, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Four Hand Massage", "image": "", "image_url": "https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/relaxed-young-guy-lying-couch-spa-salon-experiencing-tandem-back-massage-performed-two-expert-masseuses-relaxed-guy-346398656.jpg?w=768", "description": "Four Hand Massage is a luxurious and synchronized therapy where two skilled therapists work together in perfect harmony. Using rhythmic, flowing movements, this massage creates a deeply relaxing and immersive experience, allowing your body and mind to completely let go of stress while enhancing overall well-being.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nProvides deep relaxation and mental calm |\r\nDoubles the effectiveness of traditional massage |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nRelieves muscle tension quickly |\r\nCreates a unique, soothing sensory experience"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 19, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Couple Massage", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/7365436/pexels-photo-7365436.jpeg", "description": "Couple Massage is a relaxing and intimate experience where two people enjoy a massage together in the same room, each with their own therapist. It’s perfect for partners, friends, or loved ones looking to unwind, reconnect, and share a soothing wellness experience in a calm and luxurious environment.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nEnhances bonding and connection |\r\nReduces stress and promotes relaxation |\r\nCreates a shared memorable experience |\r\nImproves mood and emotional well-being\r\nRelieves muscle tension for both individuals"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 20, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Gel Massage 💧", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/19641811/pexels-photo-19641811.jpeg", "description": "Gel Massage is a refreshing and soothing therapy that uses specially formulated massage gels to provide a smooth, cooling sensation on the skin. The lightweight texture allows for effortless gliding while deeply relaxing the muscles, making it perfect for relieving heat, stress, and fatigue. This massage leaves your body feeling cool, refreshed, and revitalized.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nProvides a cooling and refreshing effect |\r\nRelieves muscle tension and fatigue |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nHydrates and softens the skin |\r\nPromotes relaxation and stress relief"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 21, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Potli Massage", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/6187837/pexels-photo-6187837.jpeg", "description": "Potli Massage is a traditional Ayurvedic therapy that uses warm herbal pouches (potli) filled with medicinal herbs, oils, and spices. These heated bundles are gently pressed and massaged over the body to relieve pain, reduce stiffness, and promote deep relaxation. The warmth and herbal essence work together to detoxify and rejuvenate your body naturally.\r\n\r\n✨ Benefits:\r\n\r\nRelieves muscle and joint pain |\r\nReduces stiffness and inflammation |\r\nImproves blood circulation |\r\nDetoxifies the body naturally |\r\nPromotes deep relaxation and healing"}}, {"model": "api.service", "pk": 22, "fields": {"category": 1, "name": "Signature Therapy", "image": "", "image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/19641837/pexels-photo-19641837.jpeg", "descript